    "media_with_text_XEXjw9": {
      "type": "media-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_WUP6tU": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Better Spinal Support",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "heading_h1": false
          }
        },
        "text_mYEqzW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Designed to promote better spinal alignment and overall sleep posture, our orthopaedic mattresses provide medium firm, consistent support across the entire body. They help distribute weight evenly, reducing pressure on key areas such as the back, hips and shoulders, which can ease everyday aches and joint discomfort.</p><p>Orthopaedic mattresses are especially suitable for back and stomach sleepers. Crafted using durable materials and supportive comfort layers, they maintain their shape over time, ensuring long-lasting comfort and reliable performance.</p><p></p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
