          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "enable_media": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Fast_Delivery_14_9f639147-c019-4bd4-9c01-4ad71774f8af.png",
            "media_scale": 100,
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h3>Silent Spring System</h3><p>Our orthopaedic mattresses with silent spring technology offer medium firm support for proper spinal alignment. The noise-free spring system reduces movement transfer, making it ideal for shared beds, while durable comfort layers provide long-lasting support and comfort.</p>",
