            "media_scale": 100,
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h3>Easy Maintenance and Care</h3><p>Our Orthopaedic mattress is designed for easy maintenance and care, with removable and washable covers available for select models. Keep your mattress fresh and clean with minimal effort.</p>",
